title: Teen testifies about defying mom to get vaccinated
description: Ethan Lindenberger, an 18-year-old whose mother opposes vaccines, testified before a Senate committee about how he decided to get vaccinated and what he learned about the importance of immunizing against infectious diseases like measles. Watch his opening remarks.
